        "creation_date": 1357884952,
        "body": "<p>Apache POI uses HSSFWorkbook object for creating xls files and XSSFWorkbook object for xlsx files. Please check what object you used for creating xls.<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://poi.apache.org/spreadsheet/quick-guide.html\">http://poi.apache.org/spreadsheet/quick-guide.html<\/a><\/p>\n",
